Class GTBaseMessageData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gotenna.sdk.data.messages.GTBaseMessageData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GTMessageDataProtocol
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GTBinaryMessageData, GTFrequencySlotData, GTGroupCreationMessageData, GTLocationOnlyMessageData, GTLocationRequestOnlyMessageData, GTTextOnlyMessageData

    public abstract class GTBaseMessageData
extends java.lang.Object
implements GTMessageDataProtocol
    The base class that all message data classes should inherit from. Created on 2/9/15.
